From: OpenMandriva
Subject: [PATCH] NANCY: Fix -Werror=format-security in SortPuzzle debug cheat

debug() is a printf-style function; passing a non-literal format
string fails with -Werror=format-security.

--- a/engines/nancy/action/puzzle/sortpuzzle.cpp	2026-06-20 17:59:46.000000000 +0200
+++ b/engines/nancy/action/puzzle/sortpuzzle.cpp	2026-07-18 21:07:41.210199775 +0200
@@ -293,7 +293,7 @@
 				const Cell &cur = _current[r][c];
 				line += Common::String::format("%d ", cur.value);
 			}
-			debug(line.c_str());
+			debug("%s", line.c_str());
 		}
 		debug("-----");
 	}
